                            <comment id="270240" author="adilger" created="Thu, 14 May 2020 18:11:29 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Being able to read the &quot;&lt;tt&gt;dump_namespace&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; file directly with &quot;&lt;tt&gt;lctl get_param&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; (via debugfs, similar to &lt;tt&gt;lite.&amp;#42;.dump_pages&lt;/tt&gt;) instead of dumping it to the debug log and having to read it from there would be way better. &lt;/p&gt;</comment>
